How Helm Works Internally

    We will understand the complete flow:

    Developer
        │
        ▼
    helm install
        │
        ▼
    Read Chart.yaml
        │
    Read values.yaml
        │
    Read templates/
        │
    Replace template variables
        │
    Generate Kubernetes YAML
        │
    Send YAML to Kubernetes API Server
        │
    Pods Created

